   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">
         <fig class="- topic/fig ">
            <title class="- topic/title ">Fastening set for bottom IP kit</title>
            <image href="../../Images/Bottom_IP_Kit_Grid-kit_0000392130.svg"
                   placement="inline"
                   class="- topic/image "/>
         </fig>
         <note class="- topic/note ">The fastening sets for the bottom IP kit is delivered
in kit 1 (0H-9209).</note>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The bottom front and back grids are fastened
with two sets consisting of:</p>
         <table class="- topic/table ">
            <tgroup cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup ">
               <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="20.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="40.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="20.00mm" class="- topic/colspec "/>
               <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">Position:</entry>
                     <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">Parts:</entry>
                     <entry valign="top" class="- topic/entry ">Quantity:</entry>
                  </row>
               </thead>
               <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">Screw</entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">1</entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">Washer</entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">1</entry>
                  </row>
                  <row class="- topic/row ">
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(C)</b>
                     </entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">Fastening clip</entry>
                     <entry class="- topic/entry ">1</entry>
                  </row>
               </tbody>
            </tgroup>
         </table>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The procedure is the same for all types of bottom IP kits;
grids, gland plates and/or filter mats.</p>
      </context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Slide in any bottom grids, gland plates and/or filter mats <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(D)</b> on the rails under the transport unit.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <note class="- topic/note ">Depends on the system configuration, the selected IP rating
and terminal/cable inlet placement.</note>
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image href="../../Images/Bottom_IP_Kit_Fit-plates_0000392129.svg"
                         placement="inline"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">
               <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Only for gland plates (Not used):</b> Fit the screws
attaching the gland plates <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(D)</b> to the sockets at the locations <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(E)</b>.</cmd>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Fit the clips <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(C)</b>. Fit the screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>, the
washers <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(B)</b> and the front grid <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(F)</b> to the clips <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(C)</b>. Screw in and tighten the screws <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(A)</b>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image href="../../Images/Bottom_IP_Kit_Fit-front-grid_0000392128.svg"
                         placement="inline"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Fit the back grid <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(G)</b> in the same way as the front
grid <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(F)</b>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <fig class="- topic/fig ">
                  <image href="../../Images/Bottom_IP_Kit_Fit-back-grid_0000392127.svg"
                         placement="inline"
                         class="- topic/image "/>
               </fig>
            </info>
         </step>
      </steps>
